descriptionHtml:
"Reports for Followers'' as an Instagram tracker app provides significant insights for Instagram account related to each post, followers & activity information. Tracking insights will get a comprehensive report of growth trends for you and you will be able to experience useful analysis tools to find a better knowledge of your account, such as below question:
- Curious who would be your best friend?
- Have no idea of low account engagement?
- Which type of posts are popular and should be scheduled next?
- Wondering what is the best memorable moment of past time?

REPORTS FOR FOLLOWERS WILL HELP YOU FIND OUT THE ANSWER
The key features:
- Profile Tracker to Get Followers Analytics (Followers Lost/ Gained)
- Profile Followers Insights (Who Do Not Follow Me Back/ Who You Are Not Follow Back/Who Blocked You/Who Unfollowed You)
- Get Detailed Insights for Posts and Stories (Your Best & Worst Posts/Check Your Most Popular Insta Posts and Stories.)
- Track Insta Account Growth Trends (Followers, New Following, Likes, Comments, etc.)
- View Your Followers Insights (Top Liker/Top Commenter/Most Profile Tagged)
- View Your Best Followers and Ghost Followers( Who You May Interest /Your Secret Admirers)
- Popularity Shows Each Tags Importance Rate of the Posts.
- AI insight that explores your unknown spirit, visual wonders with AI Insight of account.
- The Best Moment features that allow you to easily store the most past memorable moment!

Download the app and give a complete analysis into your own account, and manage your account effectively.

•storage/SD card : To store the image generated by the app for sharing purpose
